	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Mar 23rd 2:02 PM 2003</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would like to first start of by saying that THE most common question most people ask is I am a level &lt;##&gt; where should I level now.Therefore I would like to suggest we take a Idea from another great site and start a level history thread here.Reply to this post and each one of you no matter what your level, list out your leveling history.As you gain levels just come back and edit your original reply.In this manner many other necro's in the years to come will view what I hope is tons of posts that show a breakdown of where we all leveled.Also any notes etc that you feel important you could list to the side.If your over level 10 you need to be posting here.Lets give this a go and see what type of results we can produce.List out your race as sometimes that may effect where you are suggesting someone level.That said here we go.......<br><br>Baron Boneklaw Von`Torment<br>Iksar Necromancer on Sullon Zek<br><br>1-6&nbsp;&nbsp;Field of Bone(newb garbabe near city,scaled pups etc)<br><br>6-10 Field of Bone(pit area, lower end,Pull singles to ramp,scorpions,bugs,bandits,skellies)<br><br>10-15 FoB- Kurns Tower super xp dungeon bonus, skellies on ent,2nd,3rd floor)<br><br>15-20 FoB-Kurns Tower-OUTSIDE park pet back of tower pull singles to tower wall to fight,heartstings,skellies,bugs,etc{if in trouble can run up ramp to zone into kurns &gt;;O  }<br><br>1-20 guide on FOB <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104474742062478" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104474742062478</a><br><br>20-21 Warslike Woods- Giant fort&quot;Grouped&quot; or can do Overthere(OT) mudpit area Soloed or Grouped<br><br>21-29 Warslike Woods- &quot;SOLO&quot; Brutes of Dalnir caves,soloed the brutes from 21-29 working the 3 spawn and 2 spawn room camp.Head like your going to Dalnir zone and in the same set of caves are 2 rooms with Brutes.<br><br>29-40 Overthere (OT) &quot;SOLO&quot; necro &quot;fear-kite&quot; heaven,lots of mobs everywhere I parked on the west wall in the tree line and pulled to my pet,at 34 head further south to the Skyfire ramp area and at 36 go the Frontier Mountain zone ledge.Mobs are increasingly harder and more plentiful the further south you go...<br><br>31-36 (alternate location, didnt use but could have) Iceberg in Timordious Deep (TD) bottom part of the zone...long swim excellent xp though<br><br>40-44 Emerald Jungle (EJ) rarely populated, you can set up a nice camp on the ledge at the ent to the zone from FOB, look for a set of ruins following the ledge North after the zone in..you will see a building and a column that has fallen..it looks like a RAMP from the side..if you dont see this your at the wrong set of ruins..head further north from the ramp and set camp in the small clearing just north of the mentioned ruins.Fear pathing is wonderful,if you get adds (and sometimes you do) the fear pathing allows you to handle up to 3 kites at a time...yeah I did it I know :) Targets here are roamers that come by from the cliff below and from the stairs that lead down to the drop off...plenty passing by to keep you busy.<br><br>44-51 Lake of Ill Omen Bloodgills, I have a DETAILED guild on this camp under necromancer classes here.<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104480917167413" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104480917167413</a><br><br>51-53 Scarlet Desert(luclin) set up camp at the zone tunnel to THE GREY. Pull scarlet cheetas, blood tribe warriors, shammans, sunflowers, etc, can fear kite here with no trouble if you pull back to tunnel ent and fear...<br><br>52-58 Alternate xp spot Jagged Pine see below<br><br>53-54 Twilight Sea- (dock people) I also got 6 AA here as well.There is a small island that has two docks on it with 3 npc's/dock pulled them and then accross the water to Katta zone,Pulled the two bards on the stone dock and the 2 guards at the entrance to katta zone... NOTE: as of the LoY expansion date, this camp is messed up majorly, however with some careful pulling can still be done. I would suggest now to do HHK nobles or Start Jagged Pine at a earlier time than I did.<br><br>51-55 Guide on TS dock people<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104844490916136" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104844490916136</a><br><br>51-55 Guide on HHK Nobles<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104844539016095" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104844539016095</a><br><br>54-58....and still going ..Jagged Pine..Gnoll caves. Hurry before they nerf the MOST excellent spot for necros I have ever seen.I will try to write or copy a guide on this spot.The camp is the trap drop down area in the Gnoll caves.Northern most part of Jagged Pine zone.Note Oracle gnolls..see invisible.I wish I had found this spot at 52 or so.At 57 (current) the warriors still con dk blue and I can keep 8 in single pull rotation til the spawn repops.<br><br>53-58 Guide on Jagged Pine Gnolls<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104844598816270" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/classes.html?class=14&amp;mid=104844598816270</a><br><br>EDITED 3/28/03<br>Hit 58 at the gnolls of jagged pine, now I am in PoJ soloing and some duoing Prisoners.Solo they provide around a blue tick or so with of course duoing being slightly less.Really 59+ I am starting to think grouped is the way to go til 65...GOOD luck to you dark ones...hope this thread will help, <br><br>PLEASE&gt;&gt;&gt; only post leveling history here and put your comments at the bottom of your post that way others can print this entire thread for a guide on planning out there own &quot;Life as a Necro&quot; thanks....Da' Bone <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Mar 28 16:20:15 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Boneklaw Von`Torment<br>I live in the shadows, I'm hated & rejected,I command the dead,I control disease,I alter blood,I give life & I take it away, I'm the culmination of all you fear,I am Necromancer</td></tr>
