	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;   Ok I have seen alot of desent guides for necros BUT none for 1-65. I think it wold do a lot for us necros if someone posted some guides like this.<br>     What I wold like to see is something for NONE TWIEAKED necros that has some farely descript idias.But for now I will tell how I got to 25 in less than 2 weeks.<br>Ok start by Hunting FoB(field of bone) I sugust binding in PoK(plane of knolage) FoB has a good exp bonus so it's grate for lower lvls. Hunt there till about 11 then move to the tower just off of the pit. You can rack in bone chips like a mofo and get the Karnak exp bonus plus a dungen bonus. Do that till about 15 and move to PC(Pludel caverns) and invis to get past the first set of tents. After passing the tents turn to the right and you'll see a little pece of land that sticks out move there and set up camp. There are 2 mobs that you can pull with ease a shroom on the ledge and a bandet fisherman on the end on the pece of land. Camp that till they turn LB(light blue) out then invis again and move up the ledge to the left of where you come in if you see ugly lizard type things you went the wrong way. But if you go the right way you should run in to another bunch of tents refered to as C2(Camp 2). Go stright threw that camp do not stop behind the camp theres a ledge with 2 or 3 bandets that you can camp till 25. Good luck.<br><br>Knoxmortis 16 Bringer of death<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
